													<LONG-NAME>
														<L-4 L="EN">Standard Test - Startup</L-4>
													</LONG-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Enables OS Startup test for the Unit Under Test (OS Core).
The OS Startup test is instantiated for the referenced OS Test Communication Task Ref.
For detailed information regarding the demands on the referenced OsTask refer to the description of the vItaHlpOsTestCommunicationTaskRef parameter.</L-2>
													</DESC>
