													<SHORT-NAME>vItaHlpFlsStandardTestFlsCompare</SHORT-NAME>
													<LONG-NAME>
														<L-4 L="EN">Standard Test - Flash Compare</L-4>
													</LONG-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Enables the Flash Compare test for the Unit Under Test (FlsSector).
Requires the following APIs from the Fls module to be enabled:
   - /Fls/FlsGeneral/FlsCompareApi
   - /Fls/FlsGeneral/FlsGetJobResultApi</L-2>
