													<LONG-NAME>
														<L-4 L="EN">Standard Test - Clock Timing</L-4>
													</LONG-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Enables the MCU Clock Timing test.
The MCU Clock Timing test requires an OS alarm with a configured OsAlarmAction OsAlarmActivateTask. The referenced task must not be used/activated by the RTE/BRE during execution of vItaHlp.
Moreover, the referenced task must not be used by another vItaHlp test module.
The task implementation is provided by vItaHlp.</L-2>
													</DESC>
