													<LONG-NAME>
														<L-4 L="EN">Canoe Channel Name</L-4>
													</LONG-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Set the name as configured in the CANoe network.
Do not use CANoe keywords (Eth1...Eth32) as channel name. Generally avoid using similar constructs like Eth0, Eth00, etc. for channel names.

Note: Please take care that the Canoe Channel names are consistent (e.g. use the same Canoe Channel name if TestCom and Eth Test Module references the same Eth Controller). </L-2>
													</DESC>
